        "timestamp": 1753334732
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>There is now a graph structure which allows for loops so that would be a way, but this is very recent and there is none of the useful tools from simplegraphs yet. I might work on bringing some of these there as I need them for graphs with loops and multiedges myself.</p>",
